name: wtfJustHappenedTodaycom
0:
”Alexa, ask 'What the F. just happened today?'”
”Alexa, open What the F. Just Happened”
”Alexa, ask 'What the F. just happened in politics?'”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: what the f. just happened
des:
If you find yourself hearing a political story these days, and asking "...WTF just happened?", then this is the perfect addition to your Alexa.

Keep up to date with the latest in United States political news with this unbiased daily digest of the Trump campaign's full-court-press approach to governance.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
